Fix motion inputs, add z position variable
Addition of some QoL features and added simple implementation of more advanced movement options in CASP

Update: Register inputs during freeze frames (#53)
* Update CastagneEngine.gd
Add input step during freeze frames
* Update CMInput.gd
Makes it so inputs done during freeze frames are stored and performed on the first frame after.
* Add new tool to display frame data
Adds in a frame data display tool to the editor.
* Update CMInput.gd
Fixed bug where first frame of blockstun could be canceled into an attack due to the way inputs were stored during freeze
* Delete CETool-FrameData.tscn
* Delete CETool-FrameData.gd
Created new branch dev in Atlinx/castagne
